<item>
            <title>[FELIX-905] Felix needs an RFC 126 FindHook</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/FELIX-905</link>
                <project id="12310100" key="FELIX">Felix</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;RFC 126 defines a FindHook that Felix needs to implement.&lt;br/&gt;
For more information see: &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.osgi.org/download/osgi-4.2-early-draft2.pdf&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://www.osgi.org/download/osgi-4.2-early-draft2.pdf&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
